(49, 'en', 'Rambutan', 'rambutan', 46, 81, '/upload/images/Product/chomchom.jpg', '', '<p>Raucuquachaua.com specializes in providing order products for restaurants and hotels with safe, quality foods, fast and on-time delivery.</p>', '<p>Rambutan is a tropical fruit, grown a lot in the Mekong Delta, especially Ben Tre. This is a familiar fruit in life, the fruit when ripe has a bright red skin. When enjoying, you will feel the succulent meat, sweet taste and crunchy texture.<br />\r\nNot only attractive in taste, rambutan also contains many nutrients such as: vitamin C, copper, manganese, potassium, calcium, iron, phosphorus, fiber, ... Therefore, this is a very good fruit for health. capable of beautifying women.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>USES OF RAMBOO</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rambutan contains a lot of water, so it helps to cool down the body</li>\r\n	<li>High in fiber and low in calories, it keeps you full for a long time, controls hunger pangs and is a good support for a weight loss plan.</li>\r\n	<li>Manganese nutrients along with vitamin C in rambutan help support collagen production, and act as an antioxidant to help protect skin, moisturize skin,</li>\r\n	<li>The abundant phosphorus content in rambutan helps stimulate cell growth and helps eliminate wastes and toxins in the kidneys.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Rambutan is a fruit that has many good uses for the body, but eating about 5 fruits a day only, eating too much will lead to heat in the body and not good for the digestive system.</p>', 'SP0049', 25000, NULL, 0, 0, 'g', '[46]', 'W1siMSJdLFsiMiJdLFtbIjYiXV1d', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '{\"weight\":null,\"length\":null,\"width\":null,\"height\":null}', '2022-12-07 09:11:17', '2022-12-15 08:46:24', 7, 7),
(50, 'en', 'Durian fruit', 'durian-fruit', 46, 81, '/upload/images/Product/saurieng.jpg', '', '<p>Raucuquachaua.com specializes in providing order products for restaurants and hotels with safe, quality foods, fast and on-time delivery.</p>', '<p>Durian is a tropical fruit with a large size and strong smell, so not everyone can eat it. However, if you are a durian, you will love this fruit.</p>', 'SP0050', 30000, NULL, 0, 0, 'g', '[46]', 'W1siMSJdLFsiMiJdLFtbIjYiXV1d', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '{\"weight\":null,\"length\":null,\"width\":null,\"height\":null}', '2022-12-07 09:12:24', '2022-12-15 08:46:37', 7, 7),
(51, 'en', 'Vietnamese Apples', 'vietnamese-apples', 46, 81, '/upload/images/Product/taota.jpg', '', '<p>Raucuquachaua.com specializes in providing order products for restaurants and hotels with safe, quality foods, fast and on-time delivery.</p>', '<p>Tamarind or sour apple (two-part nomenclature: Ziziphus mauritiana) is a tropical fruit tree, belonging to the Apple family (Rhamnaceae). In China, it is called sour apple, Indian apple or Dien apple (Yunnan apple), Yunnan hawthorn. Trees can grow very quickly even in dry areas and grow up to 12 meters tall and reach a lifespan of 25 years. It is native to Asia (mainly India) although it can also be found in Africa. The fruit is a nut, when ripe it is soft, contains a lot of water, has a sweet taste. The fruits ripen at different intervals even on just one plant and are pale green when green and pale yellow when ripe. The size and shape of the fruit depends on different varieties in the wild as well as the type grown. The fruit is eaten when ripe, soaked in wine or used to make drinks. It is a nutrient-rich fruit and contains a lot of vitamin C.</p>', 'SP0051', 50000, '0.00', 0, 0, 'g', '[46]', 'W1siMSJdLFsiMiJdLFtbIjYiXV1d', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '{\"weight\":null,\"length\":null,\"width\":null,\"height\":null}', '2022-12-07 09:13:31', '2023-09-15 04:42:14', 7, 7),
