(59, 'en', 'Celery', 'celery', 50, 81, '/upload/images/Product/cantay.jpg', '', '<p>Raucuquachaua.com specializes in providing order products for restaurants and hotels with safe, quality foods, fast and on-time delivery.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Celery brings a lot of essential nutrients to the body, so it has the ability to prevent some dangerous diseases, especially high blood pressure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Not only is it an ingredient used to prepare many delicious dishes, celery also brings a lot of essential nutrients to the body, so it has the ability to prevent some dangerous diseases, especially high blood pressure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">According to the World Health Organization (WHO), hypertension affects the health of more than 1 billion people worldwide and is the most important cardiovascular risk factor associated with coronary heart disease, heart failure, heart disease, and coronary artery disease. cerebrovascular disease and chronic kidney disease.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">It has been determined that 100g of celery leaves contain up to 6.3% protein; 0.6% lipids; 2.1% trace minerals (such as: calcium, phosphorus, iron); The fruit contains aromatic essential oils: limonene and metabolites of sadanolic acid. In addition to minerals, vitamins and nutrients, celery also contains a large proportion of hormones and essential oils, so it has a distinctive and strong aroma. Vegetable seeds help fight flatulence, bloating, stimulate excretion, increase urine output and especially increase sex drive.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Because it is rich in potent substances, celery is also known as celery, which means \"fast-acting\" in Latin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Treatment of high blood pressure: Celery contains calcium, iron, phosphorus, rich in protid (double that of other vegetables), many free amino acids, essential oils, mannitol, inositol, many vitamins, helping to increase cravings. eat, promote blood circulation, strengthen immunity and nourish the brain. Celery contains the natural chemical apigenin, which helps prevent high blood pressure and helps dilate blood vessels. Many studies have proven that celery has a significant effect on lowering blood pressure, the duration of maintenance depends on the dose more or less and on each subject.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">How to use: Take a sharp celery juice and drink it daily (divided into 3 times) and drink it until your blood pressure is stable. Or, using crushed fresh celery juice, adding a little honey and malt sugar, the same amount, heating it warm and drinking immediately, also results in a marked reduction in blood pressure. Celery uses the whole body 50g, cut about knuckles, pour 3 bowls of water, take a bowl, drink 3 times a day like that. After a short time, the blood pressure will stabilize.</p>', 'SP0059', 30000, NULL, 0, 0, 'g', '[50]', 'W1siMSJdLFsiMiJdLFtbIjgiXV1d', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '{\"weight\":null,\"length\":null,\"width\":null,\"height\":null}', '2022-12-07 09:25:44', '2022-12-15 08:49:44', 7, 7),
